    <item>
      <title>Meta 的乐观收益为 AI 投资带来回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/meta-reports-better-than-expected-quarterly-advertising-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 周三公布第二季度销售额好于预期，表明该公司在人工智能方面的投资有助于其销售更具针对性的广告。周四交易中，该公司股价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/meta-reports-better-than-expected-quarterly-advertising-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 20:08:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
